text: Paul Lüönd (15 April 1950 - 3 April 2014) was a Swiss musician and politician. He formed a group with his older two brothers called Mosibuäbe. Lüönd grew up in the Mosi on Ingenbohl. He died on 3 April 2014 from a long illness in Switzerland, aged 63.Zum Tod von Paul Lüönd (1950-2014) ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1950 births Category:2014 deaths Category:People from Schwyz Category:Swiss musicians Category:Swiss politicians
